{
  "stem": "9730.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, in those days, there-- there was no money for that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's name was Alice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her maiden name was Nahm, N-A-H-M.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she-- she was very kind, with a good sense of humor, and very, very industrious, and always trying to help in every area where it was needed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She also cared a great deal for others and helped others wherever she could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this, of course, was later to come into play even more as conditions grew worse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had no occupation per se, but she would conduct some small business to help along with the family finances.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't forget, these were very rough times between the two World Wars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Germany was economically [BACKGROUND NOISE] tremendously depressed, which affected everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially the-- the-- the unchecked, wild inflationary period in the early '20s ruined so many businesses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, my father was suffering from that, also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we always had a standard Shabbos dinner, you might say, which would start out with-- with fish and soup, and-- and then possibly a pot roast or something like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- you know, it was simply expected that we would always have a regular Shabbos dinner with wine, and naturally, with [NON-ENGLISH] and the usual rituals.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Passover we usually had in our home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it could happen that someone else might invite us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we-- we always gave a seder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that that-- you know, that followed the-- the-- all the rituals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while we were not ultra-orthodox, we we-- we were observant, and were what you might consider conservative.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- I-- I do remember certain incidents from-- from seders.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
